{"tid":1503384,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"電腦白痴想買部notebook比女朋友","createTime":"2019-08-25T03:21:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T08:50:45.000Z","uid":275567,"like":9,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"9a92d5e799451144e6b22568a5e17f1b310e00a2","tid":1503384,"uid":275567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T03:21:06.000Z","msg":"如題<br />\nBudget $5k<br />\n打到lol就得<br />\n平時都係用黎打下lol睇下劇<br />\n輕身少少當然最好<br />\n<br />\n唔好屌我5k學咩人買電腦住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同女朋友出左黎住個個月生活費都去得份糧7788<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n$5k力已盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n女朋友以前好鍾意打機<br />\n自從搬出黎同我住之後幾乎冇掂過電腦咁滯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黎緊佢就黎生日想買部notebook送比佢<br />\n因為屋企冇位所以只能夠選擇notebook<br />\n<br />\n跪求各位巴打俾啲意見小弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15ba6f447f151208619d2447479554e6f8e39af1","tid":1503384,"uid":297236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T03:21:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://carousell.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcarousell.com&d=BuHjiuEPdik8Oboe2oqRUJktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=4e1a326b\" target=\"_blank\">carousell.com</a>"},{"pid":"326034646cc49fa487c076c23ac2fb322f5fbee8","tid":1503384,"uid":22362,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T03:22:41.000Z","msg":"小小位都冇咩<br />\n5k真係買台機好過"},{"pid":"80faa97b057bd0a691a9de6ad3c12548f4aacd8d","tid":1503384,"uid":275567,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"326034646cc49fa487c076c23ac2fb322f5fbee8","tid":1503384,"uid":22362,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T03:22:41.000Z","msg":"小小位都冇咩<br />\n5k真係買台機好過"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-0